title: Minns backtracks on right to hunt over fears it could lead to US-style gun future
summary: The NSW premier initially backed a controversial bill permitting recreational hunters to hunt feral animals on public lands. title: Tom Phillips, fugitive father on run with children for nearly four years, shot dead by NZ police in exchange of fire
